{"id":110,"parent_id":95,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":110,"title":"Acts 15","subtitle":"","short_title":"Acts","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 15"],[".studySummary",["i","Great dissension arises at Antioch concerning circumcision—The Apostles at Jerusalem decide the issue—Paul chooses Silas as his companion."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.1","order":"03.07.015.13499"},["b","1"],"And certain men which came down from Judæa taught the brethren,",["i","and said,"],"Except ye be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"circumcised"],"after the manner of Moses, ye cannot be saved."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.2","order":"03.07.015.13500"},["b","2"],"When therefore Paul and Barnabas had no small dissension and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"disputation"],"with them, they determined that Paul and Barnabas, and certain other of them, should go up to Jerusalem unto the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"apostles"],"and elders about this question."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.3","order":"03.07.015.13501"},["b","3"],"And being brought on their way by the church, they passed through Phenice and Samaria, declaring the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"conversion"],"of the Gentiles: and they caused great joy unto all the brethren."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.4","order":"03.07.015.13502"},["b","4"],"And when they were come to Jerusalem, they were received of the church, and",["i","of"],"the apostles and elders, and they declared all things that God had done with them."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.5","order":"03.07.015.13503"},["b","5"],"But there rose up certain of the sect of the Pharisees which believed, saying, That it was needful to circumcise them, and to command",["i","them"],"to keep the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"law"],"of Moses."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.6","order":"03.07.015.13504"},["b","6"],"¶And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"apostles"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"elders"],"came together for to consider of this matter."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.7","order":"03.07.015.13505"},["b","7"],"And when there had been much",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"disputing"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"Peter"],"rose up, and said unto them, Men",["i","and"],"brethren, ye know how that a good while ago God made choice among us, that the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"Gentiles"],"by my mouth should hear the word of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"gospel"],", and believe."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.8","order":"03.07.015.13506"},["b","8"],"And God, which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"knoweth"],"the hearts, bare them witness, giving them the Holy Ghost, even as",["i","he did"],"unto us;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.9","order":"03.07.015.13507"},["b","9"],"And put no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"difference"],"between us and them,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"purifying"],"their hearts by faith."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.10","order":"03.07.015.13508"},["b","10"],"Now therefore why",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"tempt"],"ye God, to put a yoke upon the neck of the disciples, which neither our fathers nor we were able to bear?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.11","order":"03.07.015.13509"},["b","11"],"But we believe that through the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"grace"],"of the Lord Jesus Christ we shall be saved, even as they."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.12","order":"03.07.015.13510"},["b","12"],"¶Then all the multitude kept silence, and gave audience to Barnabas and Paul, declaring what miracles and wonders God had wrought among the Gentiles by them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.13","order":"03.07.015.13511"},["b","13"],"¶And after they had held their peace, James answered, saying, Men",["i","and"],"brethren, hearken unto me:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.14","order":"03.07.015.13512"},["b","14"],"Simeon hath declared how God at the first did visit the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Gentiles"],", to take out of them a people for his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"name"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.15","order":"03.07.015.13513"},["b","15"],"And to this agree the words of the prophets; as it is written,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.16","order":"03.07.015.13514"},["b","16"],"After this I will return, and will build again the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"tabernacle"],"of David, which is fallen down; and I will build again the ruins thereof, and I will set it up:"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.17","order":"03.07.015.13515"},["b","17"],"That the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"residue"],"of men might seek after the Lord, and all the Gentiles, upon whom my name is called, saith the Lord, who doeth all these things."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.18","order":"03.07.015.13516"},["b","18"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Known"],"unto God are all his works from the beginning of the world."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.19","order":"03.07.015.13517"},["b","19"],"Wherefore my sentence is, that we trouble not them, which from among the Gentiles are turned to God:"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.20","order":"03.07.015.13518"},["b","20"],"But that we write unto them, that they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"abstain"],"from",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"pollutions"],"of idols, and",["i","from"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"fornication"],", and",["i","from"],"things strangled, and",["i","from"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_20d"},"blood"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.21","order":"03.07.015.13519"},["b","21"],"For Moses of old time hath in every city them that preach him, being",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"read"],"in the synagogues every sabbath day."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.22","order":"03.07.015.13520"},["b","22"],"Then pleased it the apostles and elders, with the whole church, to send chosen men of their own company to Antioch with Paul and Barnabas;",["i","namely,"],"Judas surnamed Barsabas, and Silas, chief men among the brethren:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.23","order":"03.07.015.13521"},["b","23"],"And they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"wrote"],["i",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"letters"]],"by them after this manner; The apostles and elders and brethren",["i","send"],"greeting unto the brethren which are of the Gentiles in Antioch and Syria and Cilicia:"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.24","order":"03.07.015.13522"},["b","24"],"Forasmuch as we have heard, that certain which went out from us have troubled you with words, subverting your souls, saying,",["i","Ye must"],"be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"circumcised"],", and keep the law: to whom we gave no",["i","such"],"commandment:"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.25","order":"03.07.015.13523"},["b","25"],"It seemed good unto us, being assembled with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"one"],"accord, to send chosen men unto you with our beloved Barnabas and Paul,"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.26","order":"03.07.015.13524"},["b","26"],"Men that have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"hazarded"],"their lives for the name of our Lord Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.27","order":"03.07.015.13525"},["b","27"],"We have sent therefore Judas and Silas, who shall also tell",["i","you"],"the same things by mouth."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.28","order":"03.07.015.13526"},["b","28"],"For it seemed good to the Holy Ghost, and to us, to lay upon you no greater burden than these necessary things;"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.29","order":"03.07.015.13527"},["b","29"],"That ye abstain from meats offered to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"idols"],", and from blood, and from things strangled, and from fornication: from which if ye keep yourselves, ye shall do well. Fare ye well."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.30","order":"03.07.015.13528"},["b","30"],"So when they were dismissed, they came to Antioch: and when they had gathered the multitude together, they delivered the epistle:"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.31","order":"03.07.015.13529"},["b","31"],["i","Which"],"when they had read, they rejoiced for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"consolation"],"."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.32","order":"03.07.015.13530"},["b","32"],"And Judas and Silas, being prophets also themselves, exhorted the brethren with many words, and confirmed",["i","them."]],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.33","order":"03.07.015.13531"},["b","33"],"And after they had tarried",["i","there"],"a space, they were let go in peace from the brethren unto the apostles."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.34","order":"03.07.015.13532"},["b","34"],"Notwithstanding it pleased",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"Silas"],"to abide there still."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.35","order":"03.07.015.13533"},["b","35"],"Paul also and Barnabas continued in Antioch, teaching and preaching the word of the Lord, with many others also."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.36","order":"03.07.015.13534"},["b","36"],"¶And some days after Paul said unto Barnabas, Let us go again and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"visit"],"our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_36b"},"brethren"],"in every city where we have preached the word of the Lord,",["i","and see"],"how they do."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.37","order":"03.07.015.13535"},["b","37"],"And Barnabas determined to take with them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"John"],", whose surname was",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_37b"},"Mark"],"."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.38","order":"03.07.015.13536"},["b","38"],"But Paul thought not good to take him with them, who departed from them from Pamphylia, and went not with them to the work."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.39","order":"03.07.015.13537"},["b","39"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"contention"],"was so sharp between them, that they departed asunder one from the other: and so Barnabas took Mark, and sailed unto Cyprus;"],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.40","order":"03.07.015.13538"},["b","40"],"And Paul chose Silas, and departed, being recommended by the brethren unto the grace of God."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.41","order":"03.07.015.13539"},["b","41"],"And he went through Syria and Cilicia,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_41a"},"confirming"],"the churches."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.1a","order":"03.07.015.13540"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/circumcision"},"TG Circumcision"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.2a","order":"03.07.015.13542"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disputations"},"TG Disputations"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.2b","order":"03.07.015.13544"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/2.1"},"Gal. 2:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.3a","order":"03.07.015.13546"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.5a","order":"03.07.015.13548"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/5.18.16-18"},"Gal. 5:18 (16–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.6a","order":"03.07.015.13550"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"TG Church Organization"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.6b","order":"03.07.015.13552"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/elder-melchizedek-priesthood"},"TG Elder, Melchizedek Priesthood"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.7a","order":"03.07.015.13554"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disputations"},"TG Disputations"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.7b","order":"03.07.015.13556"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.7.5-7"},"D&C 7:7 (5–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.72"},"JS—H 1:72"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.7c","order":"03.07.015.13558"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/10.20.9-48"},"Acts 10:20 (9–48)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.7d","order":"03.07.015.13560"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"TG Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.8a","order":"03.07.015.13562"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.9a","order":"03.07.015.13564"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/10.34.34-35"},"Acts 10:34 (34–35)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/17.26.25-26"},"17:26 (25–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.9b","order":"03.07.015.13566"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purification"},"TG Purification"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purity"},"Purity"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.10a","order":"03.07.015.13568"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.11a","order":"03.07.015.13570"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.14a","order":"03.07.015.13572"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.10.9-10"},"Abr. 2:10 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.14b","order":"03.07.015.13574"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/name"},"TG Name"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.16a","order":"03.07.015.13576"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.11.11-12"},"Amos 9:11 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.17a","order":"03.07.015.13578"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.32"},"Moro. 7:32"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.18a","order":"03.07.015.13580"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.20a","order":"03.07.015.13582"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.25"},"Acts 21:25"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abstain"},"TG Abstain"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.20b","order":"03.07.015.13584"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pollution"},"TG Pollution"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.20c","order":"03.07.015.13586"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fornication"},"TG Fornication"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sexual-immorality"},"Sexual Immorality"],"."],["div",{"id":"20d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.20d","order":"03.07.015.13588"},["b","20d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blood-eating-of"},"TG Blood, Eating of"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.21a","order":"03.07.015.13590"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.14.14-15"},"2 Cor. 3:14 (14–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.23a","order":"03.07.015.13592"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-writing-of"},"TG Scriptures, Writing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.23b","order":"03.07.015.13594"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/16.4"},"Acts 16:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.24a","order":"03.07.015.13596"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/17.11.10-27"},"Gen. 17:11 (10–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/8.8"},"Moro. 8:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.25a","order":"03.07.015.13598"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/common-consent"},"TG Common Consent"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.26a","order":"03.07.015.13600"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/3.11"},"2 Tim. 3:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.29a","order":"03.07.015.13602"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/8.1"},"1 Cor. 8:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.31a","order":"03.07.015.13604"},["b","31a"],["span.small","GR"],"consolation, exhortation, solace, persuasion."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.34a","order":"03.07.015.13606"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.19"},"2 Cor. 1:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.1"},"1 Thes. 1:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/5.12"},"1 Pet. 5:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"36a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.36a","order":"03.07.015.13608"},["b","36a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/12.25.20-25"},"Acts 12:25 (20–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"36b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.36b","order":"03.07.015.13610"},["b","36b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/brotherhood-and-sisterhood"},"TG Brotherhood and Sisterhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.37a","order":"03.07.015.13612"},["b","37a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/13.13"},"Acts 13:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"37b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.37b","order":"03.07.015.13614"},["b","37b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.10"},"Col. 4:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/4.11"},"2 Tim. 4:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"39a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.39a","order":"03.07.015.13616"},["b","39a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/contention"},"TG Contention"],"."],["div",{"id":"41a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.41a","order":"03.07.015.13618"},["b","41a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/24.9"},"D&C 24:9"],"."]]}
